+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: lineitem.l_quantity DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                     |
|               |   Projection: avg(lineitem.l_tax), lineitem.l_linenumber, lineitem.l_quantity                                                            |
